I am not trying to be pessimistic but I just think that my life is just as horrible as it gets and nothing can changed that. I could just probably go get the Corona Virus and just die like that.

I don’t know what to do but I think for other people life is worth living and seeing it to then end.

When you try to click a name and you successfully did it, you will try to invite them and then you get kicked out of the friends list and then you keep trying until you give up and then you have to close all tabs in the friends list in either game mode and then open the one to invite friends, once you do that then you can actually click on their names and invite them without getting kicked out. It’s a really annoying bug because it can also kick you out even if you try the method of closing and opening only 1 tab. IMPORTANT: This bug leads to another bug when you are in a game and you are inviting someone and it keeps kicking you out of friends list and you keep going back in. The bug that I am going to talk about is a bug that you can’t really do anything; you basically are frozen and you see the Fortnite logo and your mouse cursor pops up and you try to click back in but it doesn’t work, I haven’t found a method to fix this without the help of Epic but all I know is that DemonJoeFrance had this bug and he clicked on a button on his keyboard and he later then fixed it right away. I will tell you what that button is once I find the fix. I will edit this when that time comes.
